                "EDEG",
                "GSPEC",
                "MOSEP",
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Stack containing",
                "Sm target foils together with other target materials",
                "and Al and Ti monitor foils were irradiated with 50",
                "MeV deuteron beam. Irradiation time: 66min, beam",
                "intensity: 120nA. 4 series of measurements with",
                "average cooling time of 6, 25, 70 and 530 hours were",
                "done. Energy degradation in the stack was calculated",
                "by using the polynomial approximation of Andersen and",
                "Ziegler. Final beam intensity was determined by",
                "monitor reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
